"Uhhhh, Beastbox, need to thrash something, uhhh, what happen to us".
Beastbox looks up to Astroblast. Astroblast turns to Motormaster, then
back, "well, before we escaped cybertron from prison, we were able to save
youre memory banks. Now we need youre help in crushing our enemies. And the
perfect oportunity has arrisen". Astroblast Transforms into rocket ship
mode. "Climb in".

Motormaster looks to the cassettes, "you guys transform to, you will fit
better" he finishes as he and Dead-End and Speedbreaker climb in. Beastbox
looks to Squawktalk, then jumps up and transforms into a cassette, easily
fitting into Motormasters palm.
